        // operation has the `x-form-file-fields` vendor extension. Each entry
        // is the leaf baseName (e.g. "audio") — matched against the last
        // bracket segment of each parameter key. Their string values are
        // treated as filenames resolved against the app's Documents dir, and
        // their contents are streamed during the upload (never loaded in RAM).
